The paper discusses the development of a DNN framework for simulation of end-to-end deep learning applications, which falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the optimization of overall performance and energy efficiency, which could fall under the categories of Systems and Control (cs.SY) and Embedded Systems (cs.ET). Additionally, the paper discusses the development of a software framework, which could fall under the category of Software Engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper discusses the use of hardware accelerators, which could fall under the category of Architecture (cs.AR).
